snippet.title: Welcome to Sivi's Factory...
snippet.description:
WISHLIST ON STEAM NOW - https://store.steampowered.com/app/3133610/Sivis_Factory/
(the game will be completely free)

Sivi's Factory is a single player first-person horror game in which you play as Felix. You are looking for your brother on the scientific factory.

JOIN THE SIVI'S FACTORY DISCORD: https://discord.gg/dEbDPmVT

YouTube -  @quad_labs
